{"_id":"DEhpn5svO8Hp3Yy9","name":"OASIS WALL","permission":{"default":0,"kDiJJdMOROJNqvmU":3},"type":"mech_system","data":{"cascading":false,"counters":[],"deployables":[],"destroyed":false,"effect":"","lid":"ms_oasis_wall","integrated":[],"license":"DUSK WING","license_level":3,"name":"OASIS WALL","source":{"id":"uxjxh4Hl1iIg58Wcx3S_m","fallback_lid":"SSC","type":"manufacturer","reg_name":"compendium|compendium"},"tags":[{"tag":{"id":"3s9x9kN8UpSVrXnvEk9Uq","fallback_lid":"tg_unique","type":"tag","reg_name":"compendium|compendium"}},{"tag":{"id":"m4L8W_LqSLTGOqxV78i-U","fallback_lid":"tg_shield","type":"tag","reg_name":"compendium|compendium"}},{"val":2,"tag":{"id":"6jesf0ZAVDoYVvILu9-je","fallback_lid":"tg_heat_self","type":"tag","reg_name":"compendium|compendium"}}],"sp":3,"uses":0,"actions":[{"lid":"act_YfwtGIwUzWBDTvc68oaAA","name":"New Action","activation":"Protocol","terse":"Terse Description","detail":"Until the start of your next turn, you can only move in straight lines; however, you create a holographic trail behind you as you move, creating a light barrier made of contiguous sections the same Size as your mech (Size 1 for Size 0.5 Mechs) in each space you move through. This barrier grants hard cover to adjacent characters, and characters that benefit from this cover also gain Resistance to energy.<br>The barrier doesn’t count as an obstruction and has Immunity to all damage. Characters may freely pass through it but not end their turns inside it, and any character that would be involuntarily moved inside the barrier stops moving if they would end their movement inside it. It lasts for the rest of the scene or until you next use this system.","cost":1,"frequency":"","init":"","trigger":"","pilot":false,"mech":true,"heat_cost":0,"synergy_locations":[],"damage":[],"range":[],"confirm":["CONFIRM undefined"],"hide_active":false,"ignore_used":false,"log":""}],"bonuses":[],"synergies":[],"description":"“Inside? What did I see inside? You think I escaped? That t