{"_id":"E0LFVpRknAe9QtKh","name":"AUTO-COOLER","permission":{"default":0,"kDiJJdMOROJNqvmU":3},"type":"mech_system","data":{"cascading":false,"counters":[],"deployables":[],"destroyed":false,"effect":"","lid":"ms_auto_cooler","integrated":[],"license":"GENGHIS","license_level":2,"name":"AUTO-COOLER","source":{"id":"3wB3mYKitmiMMsMexoSWW","fallback_lid":"HA","type":"manufacturer","reg_name":"compendium|compendium"},"tags":[{"tag":{"id":"3s9x9kN8UpSVrXnvEk9Uq","fallback_lid":"tg_unique","type":"tag","reg_name":"compendium|compendium"}}],"sp":2,"uses":0,"actions":[{"lid":"act_DjlAnRcDuxQ2GYXGEtWb5","name":"New Action","activation":"Protocol","terse":"Terse Description","detail":"As long as you don’t take damage, move, or exceed your Heat Cap, you clear all heat at the start of your next turn.","cost":1,"frequency":"","init":"","trigger":"","pilot":false,"mech":true,"heat_cost":0,"synergy_locations":[],"damage":[],"range":[],"confirm":["CONFIRM undefined"],"hide_active":false,"ignore_used":false,"log":""}],"bonuses":[],"synergies":[],"description":"The Armory-designed auto-cooler is a simple, persistent system that actively mitigates heat generation.<br>Thermal dump thresholds are determined by fleet engineers, though pilots can adjust levels on the fly – this automatic management frees the pilot up to focus on other, more pressing tactical concerns.","type":"System"},"folder":null,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"EJ4fy23yCmMZLblw","name":"LAW OF BLADES","permission":{"default":0,"kDiJJdMOROJNqvmU":3},"type":"mech_system","data":{"cascading":false,"counters":[],"deployables":[],"destroyed":false,"effect":"","lid":"ms_law_of_blades","integrated":[],"license":"MINOTAUR","license_level":3,"name":"LAW OF BLADES","source":{"id":"hlTH_kILadfAwbZJVe4hQ","fallback_lid":"HORUS","type":"manufacturer","reg_name":"compendium|compendium"},"tags":[{"tag":{"id":"3s9x9kN8UpSVrXnvEk9Uq","fallback_lid":"tg_unique","type":"tag","reg_name":"compendium|compendium"}}],"sp":2,"uses":0,"actions":[{"lid":"act_predator_prey_concepts","name":"Predator/Prey Concepts","activation":"Full Tech","terse":"Terse Description","detail":"Make a tech attack against a hostile character within Sensors. On a hit, they immediately attack a different character or object of your choice with a single weapon as a reaction. Although you choose their target and weapon, they count as attacking and taking a reaction.","cost":1,"frequency":"","init":"","trigger":"","pilot":false,"mech":true,"heat_cost":0,"synergy_locations":[],"damage":[],"range":[],"confirm":["CONFIRM Predator/Prey Concepts"],"hide_active":false,"ignore_used":false,"log":""},{"lid":"act_slave_systems","name":"Slave Systems","activation":"Full Tech","terse":"Terse Description","detail":"Make a tech attack against a hostile character within Sensors. On a hit, they immediately take one of the following actions – chosen by you – as a reaction: Boost, Stabilize, Improvised Attack, Grapple, Ram. Although you choose the action and its target (if relevant), they count as taking the action and taking a reaction.","cost":1,"frequency":"","init":"","trigger":"","pilot":false,"mech":true,"heat_cost":0,"synergy_locations":[],"damage":[],"range":[],"confirm":["CONFIRM Slave Systems"],"hide_active":false,"ignore_used":false,"log":""}],"bonuses":[],"synergies":[],"description":"<span class='horus--subtle'>[and this my final lesson: there is no mind greater than mine